Source: doover-rs
Section: misc
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Doover Team <developers@doover.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Homepage: https://doover.com
Standards-Version: 4.7.0

Package: doover-grpc
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Replaces: doover-pydoover (<< 1.10.1)
Breaks: doover-pydoover (<< 1.10.1)
Description: Command-line client for the Doover device sidecars
 Interacts with the device agent, platform interface and modbus interface over
 gRPC. This is the Rust implementation of the CLI that pydoover shipped as
 /usr/bin/pydoover; it installs that same path, so existing scripts keep
 working, alongside its own /usr/bin/doover-grpc name.
 .
 The Python library itself remains in doover-pydoover -- this package replaces
 only the command-line entry point, not `import pydoover`.
